column1: Daily Weather Observations for Murrurundi Gap, New South Wales for October 2020
Prepared at 13:00 UTC on Tuesday 12 October 2021   IDCJDW2162.202010
Some cloud observations are from automated equipment; these are somewhat different to those made by a human observer and may not appear every day.
